---
title: Salisbury Beyond Meat® Steaks in Onion Gravy with Creamy Mash and Roasted Broccoli
description: We're bringing back memories of grandma's kitchen with these Beyond Meat® steaks, smothered in onion gravy. Creamy mashed potatoes alongside are a must, while roasted broccoli finishes off the plate with a green touch.
